Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:42.52,ED-R,,0,0,0,,She said she gave all her love to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:50.91,ED-R,,0,0,0,,We dreamt a new life Some place to be at peace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:55.08,ED-R,,0,0,0,,But things changed,suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:23:01.94,ED-R,,0,0,0,,I lost my dreams in this disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:06.16,ED-R,,0,0,0,,I'm crying
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:09.29,ED-R,,0,0,0,,Missing my lover
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.29,0:23:13.56,ED-R,,0,0,0,,I don't have the power
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:17.64,ED-R,,0,0,0,,Oh my side forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:22.58,ED-R,,0,0,0,,Oh where is my lover
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:27.35,ED-R,,0,0,0,,And i got no power
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:29.98,ED-R,,0,0,0,,I'm standing alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:34.87,ED-R,,0,0,0,,no way
